OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778613067
OL,3,CAt least 15 UK air ambulances warn
OL,4,Cfuel crisis could ground lifesaving
OL,5,Cflights
OL,7,FWords by ITV News Producer Jamel Smith
OL,9,FAt least 15 air ambulance charities
OL,10,Facross the UK have warned that the US-
OL,11,FIsraeli war on Iran has more than
OL,12,Fdoubled jet fuel prices, with some
OL,13,Fwarning that reserves could run low as
OL,14,Fsoon as June.
OL,16,FJet fuel prices have doubled since the
OL,17,FUS and Israel launched their assault
OL,18,Fon Iran in late February, causing
OL,19,Faviation issues worldwide.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
