PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778613067
OL,3,CAt least 15 UK air ambulances warn
OL,4,Cfuel crisis could ground lifesaving
OL,5,Cflights
OL,7,FThe fuel is used in both commercial
OL,8,Faircraft and the turbine-powered
OL,9,Fhelicopters operated by UK air
OL,10,Fambulance services.
OL,12,FAir ambulance charities in Cornwall,
OL,13,FEast Anglia, Essex and Hertfordshire,
OL,14,FHampshire and the Isle of Wight,
OL,15,FLondon, Midlands, Scotland, Thames
OL,16,FValley, Wales, Yorkshire, Magpas,
OL,17,FWiltshire, North West, Great Western
OL,18,Fand Lincolnshire and Nottinghamshire,
OL,19,Fhave all raised concerns with ITV News
OL,20,Fabout rising fuel costs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778613067
OL,3,CAt least 15 UK air ambulances warn
OL,4,Cfuel crisis could ground lifesaving
OL,5,Cflights
OL,7,FHampshire and the Isle of Wight said
OL,8,Faviation fuel costs have risen by
OL,9,Faround 50% since the start of the
OL,10,Fmonth, equivalent to about #10,000
OL,11,Fextra per month.
OL,13,FLondon's air ambulance said costs have
OL,14,F"more than doubled since February,
OL,15,Frising by 116%."
OL,17,FIt added: "Those costs increasing
OL,18,Fmeans that we have less money to spend
OL,19,Fon other parts of our work and, as a
OL,20,Fcharity, we rely on donations from the
OL,21,Fgeneral public to cover those costs."
OL,26,@wD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
