PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778613067
OL,3,CAt least 15 UK air ambulances warn
OL,4,Cfuel crisis could ground lifesaving
OL,5,Cflights
OL,7,FMagpas Air Ambulance Chief Executive
OL,8,FDaryl Brown said fuel costs had risen
OL,9,Fby 82.5%, while Cornwall warned the
OL,10,Fprice spike would cost them an
OL,11,Fadditional #10,000 per month.
OL,13,FYorkshire has seen an increase of
OL,14,Faround 65%, costing an estimated
OL,15,F#180,000 in additional annual costs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778613067
OL,3,CAt least 15 UK air ambulances warn
OL,4,Cfuel crisis could ground lifesaving
OL,5,Cflights
OL,7,FThe National Children's Air Ambulance,
OL,8,Fthe UK's only dedicated helicopter
OL,9,Ftransfer service for ill children and
OL,10,Fbabies, has also said the price hike
OL,11,F"will add tens of thousands of pounds
OL,12,Fto our fuel budget by the end of the
OL,13,Fyear, and all our funding comes from
OL,14,Fphilanthropy".
OL,16,FBoth East Anglia and the Midlands have
OL,17,Falso raised concerns about fuel supply.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
