FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1778613067
OL,3,CAt least 15 UK air ambulances warn
OL,4,Cfuel crisis could ground lifesaving
OL,5,Cflights
OL,7,FEast Anglia's aviation partner Babcock
OL,8,Fhas assessed its current supply risk
OL,9,Fas moderate, but warned of "potential
OL,10,Favailability issues emerging from June
OL,11,Fonwards if the wider situation does
OL,12,Fnot improve."
OL,14,FMidlands chief executive Hanna
OL,15,FSebright said the charity moved
OL,16,Fquickly to fill its reserves before
OL,17,Fprices surged, but that current
OL,18,Fsupplies "are only expected to last
OL,19,Funtil June".
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
