OL,3,CAt least 15 UK air ambulances warn
OL,4,Cfuel crisis could ground lifesaving
OL,5,Cflights
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FOther charities said they are closely
OL,13,Fmonitoring the conflict in the Middle
OL,14,FEast to plan how to maintain their
OL,15,Ffuel reserves.
OL,17,FThe closure of the Strait of Hormuz, a
OL,18,Fmajor global oil shipping route, has
OL,19,Fbeen the primary driver of rising fuel
OL,20,Fprices worldwide.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
